title: BTS, Metropolitan Planning Organization Boundaries, USA, 2008
name: BTS, Metropolitan Planning Organization Boundaries, USA, 2008
description:
Abstract: The United States Metropolitan Planning Organization database is a geographic database of Metropolitan Planning Organization political boundaries.
    Purpose: The data provides users with information about the locations, names and sizes of Metropolitan Planning Organizations and is intended for use primarily with national planning applications.
